    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["host"] == "log-1.sveidas.se")
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["country"] == "${country}")
    > filter(fn: (r) => r["requester"] == "https://eidas.grandid.com/module.php/saml/sp/metadata.php/ProxySP-eIDAS-Prod-OsthammarsKommun")
    |> rename(columns: {_value: "Östhammars kommun"})
    |> group(columns: ["_value"])

from(bucket: "eidas")
    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "error-eidas-error-response" or
      r["_measurement"] == "SAML2_AUDIT_ERROR_RESPONSE")
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["host"] == "log-1.sveidas.se")
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["country"] == "${country}")
    > filter(fn: (r) => r["requester"] == "https://m00-mg-local.idp.funktionstjanster.se/samlv2/sp/metadata/0/eidas/ostragoinge")
    |> rename(columns: {_value: "Östra Göinge kommun"})
